  "name": "RPlog_Death_of_a_Planet",
  "title": "The Death of a Planet",
  "summary": "Above the planet Cochran, Grand Admiral Danik Kreldin's Imperial fleet has shattered the Griffon Alliance and pinned the retreating New Republic Second Fleet with interdictor gravity wells. Negotiating over open comms with Republic Admiral Rodriga, Kreldin agrees to a ceasefire and lowers a gravity well to let the Republic evacuate its troops and civilians, while NR fighters under Johmac Mabru, Kyrin, Malantean, Hase, and others move to escort the marine shuttles. But the bargain is a ruse: once his own ground forces are safely aboard, Kreldin orders Base Delta Zero, and the Imperial fleet, including Captain Lynae Caiton's VSD Malignant, opens a methodical orbital bombardment that targets fault lines to tear the planet apart and slaughters fleeing ships and civilians alike. The New Republic fighters scatter through the turbolaser hellstorm and flee to hyperspace as Cochran is reduced to a molten slag, the Imperial March playing in cold triumph across Kreldin's victorious fleet.",
